     <h5>Departmental External Reviews</h5> 
     <p>In 1996 the Student Life Division initiated a commitment to external reviews.&nbsp; An external review is a process where two colleagues from other respected programs from campuses across the country are invited to join a Westmont student life member and faculty member to conduct a 2-day review of an individual department.&nbsp; The feedback from these reviews has helped us improve our effectiveness in meeting learning outcomes, improve services, and identify resource priorities.</p> 
